---
import Layout from "~/layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import Hero from "~/components/widgets/Hero.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import { TextAnimate } from "~/components/magicui/text-animate";
import { BlurFade } from "~/components/magicui/blur-fade";
import FireButton from "~/components/ui/FireButton.astro";
import prayer_works from "~/assets/images/prayer/prayer_for_works.webp";
import WidgetWrapper from "~/components/ui/WidgetWrapper.astro";
import PrayerPointsList from "~/components/widgets/PrayerPointsList.astro";
import type { PrayerPoint } from "~/components/widgets/PrayerPointsList.astro";
import { getPermalink } from "~/utils/permalinks";

const { metadata, siteRebuildStatus, lang } = Astro.props;

// Prayer points data array
const prayerPoints: PrayerPoint[] = [
  {
    icon: "tabler:hammer",
    title: "Transform yourself → transform your results",
    subtitle:
      "It is stupid to expect different results while doing the same thing 🤪. Don't focus on a good container but improve the content 🎓. More expensive content naturally needs a better container 💎. Diamonds are not stored in a milk bottle, and milk is not stored in a bank 🥛🏦",
    bibleQuote:
      '"Study to shew thyself approved unto God, a workman that needeth not to be ashamed, rightly dividing the word of truth." - 2 Timothy 2:15',
    color: "orange",
  },
  {
    icon: "tabler:gift",
    title: "Your gift <span class='italic'>makes</span> room for you",
    subtitle:
      "You don't need to teach a duck to swim, it already knows how to swim 🦆.  There is always space in the air for an eagle because it flies so high 🦅. The value of a diamond will make people all around the world to look for it 🔎💎. Your gift (your inward, inbuilt ability) makes you room you don't have to struggle to get 🏆.",
    bibleQuote: `"A man's gift maketh room for him, and bringeth him before great men." - Proverbs 16:3`,
    color: "blue",
  },
  {
    icon: "tabler:building-factory-2",
    title: "Value, Productivity, Diligence",
    subtitle:
      "Unrefined gold is worth nothing, unprocessed oil is just a black paste ⚜️🛢️. Nokia 1100 was the golden standard but now a museum item ☎️. Apple _produces_ new version every year and remains on top 🍏. One operation system is for vibe coders, but multiplying and distributing it makes Microsoft the king 👑. ",
    bibleQuote:
      '"Seest thou a man diligent in his business? he shall stand before kings; he shall not stand before mean men." - Proverbs 22:29',
    color: "green",
  },
  {
    icon: "tabler:heart",
    title: "The Main Key: <span class='text-red-500'>Love for God</span>",
    subtitle:
      "A dying man will spent all his money to for a one more day, and dead man cannot win Eurojackpot ⌛🎟️. 10B spent on bombs is an outrage, but 1,000 spent on saving lives is a celebration 🤯🎉. The value of a money is dependant on the usage ⚖️. The eternal value of a soul is dependant on the love for God ❤️‍🔥",
    bibleQuote:
      '"For what shall it profit a man, if he shall gain the whole world, and lose his own soul?" - Mark 8:36',
    color: "red",
  },
  {
    icon: "tabler:ripple",
    title: "Wisdom of God for the greatest results",
    subtitle:
      "Many men can carry many logs but a cart can carry many men and logs 🪵🧺. Gideon can travail for his life with 30,000 or win without a fight with 300 🪖🏖. Surely you can get power from the devil like drunkard happiness from a beer 🍺, but wisdom of God keeps you as a counselor from Nebuchadnezzar to Cyrus 👥. ",
    bibleQuote: '"Wisdom strengtheneth the wise more than ten mighty men which are in the city." - Ecclesiastes 7:19',
    color: "purple",
  },
  {
    icon: "tabler:users",
    title: "Walk with wise → be wise.</br>Walk with fools → be a fool.",
    subtitle:
      "Jesus can die on a cross but Joseph will give Him a tomb 🍙. Paul can be the apostle of the gentiles but Barnabas will bring him to Antioch 🏛️. Israel is the chosen people but Pharaoh gave them the Goshen 𓁈⚱️. You might have lived as a worst sinner but through Jesus you are a heir of God 🤴🏻. ",
    bibleQuote: '"And Jesus increased in wisdom and stature, and in favour with God and man." - Luke 2:52',
    color: "indigo",
  },
  {
    icon: "tabler:volcano",
    title: "Prayer to change the spiritual climate",
    subtitle:
      "You can look the greatest fool but on the day of Noah's flood only your ship will be saved ⛵. You can build the greatest city but Vesuvius will bury all the Pompeii in ashes 🌋. You can build the greatest life but without prayer you will toss that great ship miniature into the sea without knowing if it is calm or raging 🌊.",
    bibleQuote:
      '"And he spake a parable unto them to this end, that men ought always to pray, and not to faint." - Luke 18:1',
    color: "yellow",
  },
];
---

<Layout lang={lang} metadata={metadata} siteRebuildStatus={siteRebuildStatus}>
  <!-- Hero Section with Full Screen Image -->
  <div class="min-h-screen relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat z-0"
      style={`background-image: url(${prayer_works.src})`}
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Gradient overlay for better text readability -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 z-5"
      style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 50%, rgba(26, 0, 36, 0.6) 80%, #1a0024 100%);"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Text overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-20 z-10"></div>

    <Hero classes={{ containerClass: "text-left relative z-20", subtitleContainerClass: "max-w-none" }}>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        <TextAnimate
          client:load
          className="text-4xl xs:text-5xl md:text-6xl xl:text-[60px] xl:leading-[64px] font-semibold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 xl:mb-[16px] font-heading text-white"
          animation="blurInUp"
          delay={1}
          duration={0.6}
          by="character"
          once={true}
          text="Prayer for Works:"
        />

        <TextAnimate
          client:load
          className="text-4xl xs:text-5xl md:text-6xl xl:text-[60px] xl:leading-[64px] font-semibold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 xl:mb-[16px] font-heading text-orange-400"
          animation="blurInUp"
          delay={1.6}
          duration={0.6}
          by="character"
          once={true}
          text="Transform Your Career"
        />

        <div class="max-w-md">
          <TextAnimate
            client:load
            className="text-xl xl:text-[20px] xl:leading-[28px] font-normal tracking-normal text-gray-200"
            animation="blurInUp"
            delay={3}
            duration={0.6}
            by="line"
            once={true}
            text="Discover a 7-Point list to transform your career through prayer for works. 🔥🔥🔥🔥"
          />
        </div>
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="subtitle">
        <div class="flex gap-4 mb-8">
          <BlurFade client:load delay={4.2} direction="up" inView>
            <FireButton
              href="#prayer-guide"
              text="7-point list for prayer for works"
              variant="primary"
              size="small"
              icon="tabler:corner-right-down"
            />
          </BlurFade>
        </div>
      </Fragment>
    </Hero>
  </div>

  <!-- 7-Point Prayer Guide Listicle -->
  <BlurFade client:load delay={5} direction="up">
    <PrayerPointsList prayerPoints={prayerPoints} />
  </BlurFade>

  <!-- Testimonies Section -->
  <WidgetWrapper id="testimonies" animated={false} containerClass="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          Real Stories of <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-red-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Prayer at Work</span
          >
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Discover how this 7-point list for prayer for work has transformed careers and brought divine favor into
          professional experts.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonies Grid - 2 Column Layout -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Left Column - First and Second Testimonies Stacked -->
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 h-full">
          <!-- Testimony 1 - Takes 2/3 height -->
          <div class="group relative flex-[2]">
            <div
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/80 to-gray-900/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700 border-orange-500/50 hover:border-orange-500/80 transition-all duration-300 h-full"
            >
              <!-- Profile Image -->
              <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
                <div
                  class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-red-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg"
                >
                  A
                  <!-- <Image
                    class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-full"
                    src={andrew}
                    alt="Showcase image"
                    width={80}
                    height={80}
                    loading="lazy"
                  /> -->
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Testimony Content -->
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="mb-6">
                  <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
                    <div class="flex space-x-1">
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    "4 years ago my PHD went to the trash bin, but now I'm a professor and my work is being published in
                    top-tier journals. Seek first the kingdom of God, and all other things shall be added to you."
                  </blockquote>
                </div>
                <div class="border-t border-gray-600 pt-6">
                  <p class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">Andrew A.</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">
                    Award-winning physician and professor (associate) of clinical epidemiology and child health
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Testimony 2 - Takes 1/3 height -->
          <div class="group relative flex-1">
            <div
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/80 to-gray-900/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-700 border-blue-500/50 hover:border-blue-500/80 transition-all duration-300 h-full"
            >
              <!-- Profile Image -->
              <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
                <div
                  class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl font-bold shadow-lg"
                >
                  G
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Testimony Content -->
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="mb-4">
                  <div class="flex justify-center mb-3">
                    <div class="flex space-x-1">
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    "I have experienced many miracles, and guidances of God in my career. I have already recognized some
                    manifestations of the wisdom of God, and I believe He will fulfill everything He has said concerning
                    me."
                  </blockquote>
                </div>
                <div class="border-t border-gray-600 pt-4">
                  <p class="text-white font-semibold">Greta J.</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Researcher, PhD student</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column - Third Testimony and CTA -->
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 h-full">
          <!-- Your Testimony CTA - Takes 1/3 height -->
          <div class="group relative flex-1">
            <div
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900/50 to-pink-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-dashed border-purple-400/50 hover:border-purple-400 transition-all duration-300 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center"
            >
              <!-- Plus Icon -->
              <div
                class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/20 to-pink-600/20 border-2 border-dashed border-purple-400/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
              >
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>

              <!-- CTA Content -->
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Your Testimony?</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                  Have the prayer for works transformed your work life already?
                </p>
                <!-- <FireButton text="Share Your Story" variant="secondary" size="small" icon="tabler:heart" /> -->
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Testimony 3 - Takes 2/3 height -->
          <div class="group relative flex-[2]">
            <div
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/80 to-gray-900/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700 border-green-500/50 hover:border-green-500/80 transition-all duration-300 h-full"
            >
              <!-- Profile Image -->
              <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
                <div
                  class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg"
                >
                  J
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Testimony Content -->
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="mb-6">
                  <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
                    <div class="flex space-x-1">
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                      <Icon name={"tabler:star-filled"} class={`w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400`} />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    "I never was interested of creating websites. Now I'm designing, and developing them for global
                    names. And this is just the tip of the iceberg of what God has spoken. We will do great exploits for
                    our God as we expand the frontiers of His kingdom before Jesus returns!"
                  </blockquote>
                </div>
                <div class="border-t border-gray-600 pt-6">
                  <p class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">Juhani J.</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">IT specialist</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="text-center mt-16 pt-16 border-t border-gray-700">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          Ready to <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-red-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Ignite Your Prayer For Works</span
          >?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Start implementing these prayer strategies today and watch God work miracles in your professional journey.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
          <FireButton
            href={getPermalink("/en/word")}
            text="What's next?"
            variant="primary"
            size="large"
            icon="tabler:rocket"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </WidgetWrapper>
</Layout>
